# To list/scan/add Wi-Fi networks:

  $ su - # login as root
  $ wpa_cli

  > scan
  > scan_results
  > list_networks
  > add_network [next-id-available]
  > set_network [id] ssid [ssid]
  > set_network [id] psk [passphrase]
  > enable_network [id]

# To configure bind9.service (the router)

## Is the service running?

  $ su - # login as root
  $ vim /etc/bind/named.conf.options
